Package: dtodo-widget
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Desktop todo widget with frosted glass effect
 A lightweight desktop todo widget built with DTK6 and Qt6.
 It features a frosted glass blur effect, color markers,
 and creation time display for todo items.
